OL,6,F"But a 10th of households faced a
OL,7,Fmortgage interest rate of at least
OL,8,F4.7%, equivalent to #490 per month,"
OL,9,Fit continued.
OL,11,FThe report said that official poverty
OL,12,Fmeasures apply a single average
OL,13,Finterest rate to all households.
OL,15,FAbsolute poverty among mortgage
OL,16,Fholders, officially 7.9% in 2022/23,
OL,17,Fis underestimated by around 70,000
OL,18,Fpeople, according to the report.
