OL,6,FIt added: "Increases in interest rates
OL,7,Fbetween December 2021 and December
OL,8,F2023 are likely to have pushed
OL,9,Fmortgagor poverty rates up by ...
OL,10,F320,000 more people, when measured
OL,11,Faccounting for variation in mortgage
OL,12,Finterest rates.
OL,14,F"But official poverty statistics,
OL,15,Fwhich apply a single average interest
OL,16,Frate to all households, will only
OL,17,Fcapture ... 230,000 of this."
OL,19,FThe IFS also pointed to evidence that
OL,20,Fmortgage rate rises have pushed some
OL,21,Fadults into financial hardship.
