OL,6,FBorrowers remortgaging in 2022 were
OL,7,Fmore likely to fall into arrears on
OL,8,Fbills than those with mortgages who
OL,9,Fhad not remortgaged, the IFS said.
OL,11,FThe analysis suggests that, once all
OL,12,Fhouseholds have remortgaged, the
OL,13,Fnumber of adults behind on bills could
OL,14,Frise by 370,000, according to the
OL,15,Freport, funded by the Joseph Rowntree
OL,16,FFoundation (JRF).
