OL,6,FSam Ray-Chaudhuri, a research
OL,7,Feconomist at IFS and an author of the
OL,8,Freport, said poverty rises had been
OL,9,Funderstated due to the unequal impact
OL,10,Fof inflation.
OL,12,FHe said: "At a time when rates of
OL,13,Fdeprivation and food insecurity have
OL,14,Frisen substantially, poverty
OL,15,Fstatistics that hide the real scale of
OL,16,Fthese increases risk policymakers
OL,17,Fmissing what is truly happening to
OL,18,Fpoverty."
