OL,6,F"The household support fund provides a
OL,7,Fvital safety net for vulnerable
OL,8,Fhouseholds struggling to buy food,
OL,9,Fheat their home and afford essentials.
OL,10,FWith the fund due to expire at the end
OL,11,Fof September, an extension is crucial
OL,12,Fto continue support for residents
OL,13,Fthrough winter.
OL,15,F"Longer term, councils want to shift
OL,16,Faway from short-term crisis support so
OL,17,Fthey can instead invest in
OL,18,Fpreventative services which improve
OL,19,Fpeople's financial resilience and life
OL,20,Fchances, underpinned by a sufficiently
OL,21,Fresourced national welfare system."
